# Frontend Refactor Rules

## Prinsip utama
Sebelum membuat komponen, hook, atau util baru — selalu cek dulu apakah 
sudah ada versi global/shared yang bisa dipakai.

Modul referensi (sudah dimigrasi): `features/petty-cash/`, `features/purchase-invoices/`.

## Cek global sebelum buat baru

### Formatter
Selalu import dari `@/lib/formatters`:
- `fmtCurrency` — format IDR, null-safe (null → "—")
- `fmtDate` — format tanggal id-ID, null-safe
- `fmtDateTime` — format tanggal + jam id-ID, null-safe
- `fmtQty` — format angka id-ID dengan desimal, null-safe
JANGAN buat `fmtCurrency`/`fmtDate` lokal di file manapun.

### UI Primitives (selalu cek `components/ui/` dulu)
Tersedia: `Button`, `Dialog`, `Input`, `Select`, `DateInput`, 
`Textarea`, `FormField`, `StatusBadge`, `Pagination`, 
`TableSkeleton`, `CardSkeleton`, `FormSkeleton`
JANGAN buat overlay modal manual (`fixed inset-0`) — pakai `Dialog`.
JANGAN buat loading spinner manual — pakai `Button loading` prop 
atau Skeleton primitives.

### Status badge
Pakai thin wrapper + `StatusBadge` + `statusMappings` (sudah ada: 
`pettyCash`, `purchaseInvoice`, `journal`, `apPayment`, `fixedAsset`, `reconciliation`).
- **Warna** → tambah di `lib/theme/statusMappings.ts` (semantic token)
- **Label** → tetap lokal di `types/{module}.status.ts`
- JANGAN hardcode `bg-*-100 text-*-700` di komponen badge
- Exception: span inline one-off di page header boleh pakai config lokal 
  (tech debt — migrasi ke `StatusBadge` saat disentuh)

### Shared components (`components/shared/`)
- `AttachmentThumbnail` — props: `filePath`, `isImage`, `bucket`, `variant`, `onClick`
- `ProductPickerModal` — picker produk
- `RejectReasonDialog` — **belum ada**; ikuti pola `PurchaseInvoiceRejectModal` / `PettyCashRejectModal`

### Hooks global
- `hooks/useSignedStorageUrl(path, bucket)` — signed URL; auto pass-through http(s)
- `lib/urlFilters/useUrlFilters` — filter ↔ URL sync
- `lib/urlFilters/useListNavigation` — list ↔ detail dengan state URL

## Pola yang sudah established

### Modal/Dialog
Prefer `Dialog` compound — **bukan** `ConfirmModal` (legacy, jangan pakai di modul baru).
```tsx
<Dialog isOpen={open} onClose={onClose} preventClose={mutation.isPending}>
  <Dialog.Header>Judul</Dialog.Header>
  <Dialog.Body>...</Dialog.Body>
  <Dialog.Footer>
    <Button variant="secondary" onClick={onClose} disabled={isPending}>Batal</Button>
    <Button variant="danger" loading={isPending} onClick={onConfirm}>Konfirmasi</Button>
  </Dialog.Footer>
</Dialog>
```
- Reject dengan textarea: `Dialog` + `FormField` + `Textarea`
- Handler di page hook (PI) atau di dalam modal (PC) — keduanya OK; 
  prefer handler di hook jika page punya banyak aksi status

### Button variants
- `primary` — aksi utama (submit, save, ajukan)
- `secondary` — aksi sekunder (batal di footer, edit)
- `danger` — aksi destruktif di footer dialog (hapus, tolak)
- `ghost` — aksi minor (back, icon-only, link-style)
- **Bukan variant baru** — pakai `className` override:
  - Hijau (setujui) → `primary` + `className="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 dark:bg-green-600 dark:hover:bg-green-700"`
  - Amber (batalkan post / gabung) → `secondary` + `className="border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 text-amber-800 hover:bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/20 dark:border-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200"`
  - Danger-ghost (hapus inline di table) → `ghost` + `className="text-red-500"` atau `text-red-600`

### FormField & Input
- Field dengan label eksplisit → `FormField` + render-props `{ inputId, describedBy }`
- Input di table cell (tanpa label) → `Input` langsung, tanpa `FormField`; 
  boleh `className="py-1 px-2 text-xs"` untuk compact
- **Gotcha:** `Input.rightIcon` punya `pointer-events-none` — tombol clear (X) 
  harus di-posisikan absolute **di luar** `Input`, bukan lewat `rightIcon`

### Tailwind JIT — DILARANG dynamic class
```tsx
// ❌ tidak aman — class tidak masuk bundle
`border-${color}-600 text-${color}-600`

// ✅ literal map di constants.ts atau types/
const TAB_COLORS: Record<string, { active: string; inactive: string }> = { ... }
```

### Page layout
`Layout.tsx` sudah constrain viewport (`h-[calc(100vh-4rem)]` + `overflow-auto` di `<main>`).
- Page root: `flex h-full min-h-0 flex-col` — **bukan** `h-screen`
- List page petty-cash: container `max-w-*` tanpa full-height — juga valid

### List page — hook split (referensi PI)
```
useXxxFilters   → useUrlFilters + toApiQuery (jika perlu transform)
useXxxList      → data + permissions + delete
useXxxSelection → multi-select / merge (jika ada)
useXxxPost      → aksi async khusus list (post/unpost, dll)
useXxxDetail    → data + derived state
useXxxDetailModals → modal visibility + mutation handlers
```

### File naming convention per feature
```
features/{module}/
├── api/          — TanStack Query hooks + API calls (JANGAN taruh di hooks/)
├── components/   — UI components (+ thin StatusBadge wrapper)
├── hooks/        — custom hooks turunan (useXxxList, useXxxForm, dll)
│   └── index.ts  — barrel export hooks public
├── types/        — interface + status labels
├── utils/        — pure functions domain (charges, filter URL, staging)
└── pages/        — compose-only, target <300 LOC
```

### Import conventions
- Prefer `@/components/ui` barrel (bukan `@/components/ui/Button` per-file)
- Prefer `@/lib/formatters`, `@/lib/theme`, `@/hooks/useSignedStorageUrl`

### Migrasi bertahap (modul baru)
1. **Fase 0** — ekstrak duplikat ke types/utils; zero UI change
2. **Fase 1** — pecah file >400 LOC ke komponen + hooks; pure move
3. **Fase 2** — migrasi primitives per komponen (Button → Input → Dialog → FormField)
4. **Fase 3** — polish: JIT classes, layout, skeleton, empty state

JANGAN gabung Fase 0+1+2 dalam satu PR untuk file yang sama.
JANGAN migrasi file besar sebelum dipecah dulu.

## Known limitations — biarkan unless diminta
- Native `<input type="checkbox">` — tidak ada Checkbox primitive
- `EmptyState` — belum ada di design system (feature-local OK, jangan buat global ad-hoc)
- `PageLoader` — belum ada; plain `"Loading..."` div acceptable
- Image preview overlay manual di detail page — minor, out of scope

## Yang TIDAK perlu diglobalisasi
- Status config domain-specific (GP line status, charge labels, file type labels)
- Form logic domain-specific (expense modes, split nota, GR selection, settlement)
- Filter field definitions per modul (parser/merge di `utils/*Filters.url.ts` tetap lokal)
- Staging invoice logic, charge calculation, totals per dokumen

## Sebelum PR / setelah rename-move
- `cd frontend && npx tsc --noEmit` → exit 0
- Grep path lama: `rg "old/path" frontend/src --glob '*.{ts,tsx}'`
